-=Awp_Eclipse=-

Awp map made in dedication to a CS:S clan named EcLiPse. It's a small map fast-paced map. Hope you will enjoy the map as much as we did.

-Features:

  • Custom textures (clan logo and other)
  • 3d skybox
  • Fully working HDR
  • Skybox Secret - Good luck with that one ;)

Good luck and have fun.
